"3:180:16" : {s: 3, a: 180, w: 16, r: "", t: "لَّهُمْ", l: "", lc: 3307, tl: "lahum", lb: "",e: "for them.", b: "তাদের জন্য, তাদের প্রতি", i: "bagi mereka", f: 31, rm: ""},
"3:180:17" : {s: 3, a: 180, w: 17, r: "طوق", t: "سَيُطَوَّقُونَ", l: "يُطَوَّقُ", lc: 1, tl: "sayuṭawwaqūna", lb: "বেষ্টন করা, ঘিরে রাখা, গলায় হার পরানো",e: "Their necks will be encircled", b: "শীঘ্রই তাদের গলায় বেড়ী বনিয়ে দেয়া হবে", i: "akan dikalungkan", f: 1, rm: "to be able, be in a position to do something. taaqatun - ability, power, strength. ataaqa (vb. 4) - to be able to do a thing. tawwaqa (vb. 2) - to twist a collar, put a neck-ring on, impose a difficult task on a person, enable, hang around neck, impose, lay upon, encircle. ataaqa (vb. 4) - to be able to do a thing, find extremely hard and difficult to bear, do a thing with great difficulty. taaqat - the utmost that a person can do."},
