"3:180:29" : {s: 3, a: 180, w: 29, r: "عمل", t: "تَعْمَلُونَ", l: "عَمِلَ", lc: 276, tl: "taʿmalūna", lb: "চিন্তাভাবনা করে কাজ করা",e: "you do", b: "তোমরা করেছো", i: "kamu kerjakan", f: 83, rm: "to do/make/act/work/operate/perform/construct/manufacture, practice a handcraft, be active, one who does."},
